### Read all products
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Products

### Update product 1 — price and stock
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Products(1)
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 35.99,
  "stock": 140
}

### Delete product 5
DELETE http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/catalog/Products(5)
Content-Type: application/json
